{"parse":{"title":"Spotted Feltail","pageid":119951,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{tooltip\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||8}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_39\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=27425\n|ilvl=60\n|name=Spotted Feltail}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThis item can be fished in [[Terokkar Forest]], [[Zangarmarsh]]  , [[The Underbog]] and [[Serpentshrine Cavern]].\n\n\n==Spotted Feltail as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Feltail Delight}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27425}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/spotted_feltail.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}